{
  "texts": [
    "Studies used continuous regression, probit, logit, and ordinal regression estimation techniques.",
    "Five studies examined the effects of receiving an offer of a private school choice scholarship or voucher, whereas the others examined the effects of self-selected private school attendance.",
    "Twelve studies used panel data while the rest used (pooled) cross-sectional data.",
    "The grade ranges of study participants varied vastly, and many studies included some or all high school years.",
    "Study samples consisted of students only (42), parents only (8), and the combination of parents and students (7)."
  ]
}